            <title>[SPR-12430] Support org.springframework.context.ApplicationContextInitializer usage programmatically (in Servlet 3.0+ environments)</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-12430</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;org.springframework.context.ApplicationContextInitializer&lt;/tt&gt; is only usable from &lt;tt&gt;context-param&lt;/tt&gt; or &lt;tt&gt;init-param&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It should also be usable programmatically, e.g. from &lt;tt&gt;WebApplicationInitializer&lt;/tt&gt; implementation:&lt;/p&gt;

